      • doneParse

        void doneParse(int numErrors)
        Called when the parsing process has been completed. The progress bar value is set to 100, the JDialog displays that the parsing process has finished, and also displays the number of errors that were found. The export button also becomes visible so that the user can export the results to a CSV file.
        Parameters:
        numErrors - The number of errors found during the parsing process
